item.title: CVE-2023-35905|2024-09-19T19:27:34.999Z -- ibm -- filenet%20content%20manager
item.description: IBM FileNet Content Manager 5.5.8, 5.5.10, and 5.5.11 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 259384.
